    "basic_qualifications": "- 5+ years of data engineering experience<br/>- 3+ years of developing and operating large-scale data structures for business intelligence analytics using ETL/ELT processes experience<br/>- 3+ years of developing and operating large-scale data structures for business intelligence analytics using data modeling experience<br/>- Experience with data modeling, warehousing and building ETL pipelines",
